---
title: Cheesy BBQ Chicken with Rainbow Slaw & Veggie Fries
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of our favourite flavours. Tender chicken breast gets a lightly spiced and saucy
coating, with carb-friendly veggie fries and a creamy slaw to round out the meal. It's the taste of nostalgic backyard
BBQ that you've been longing for!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
